project_descr: Strengthening the communities in seismic threats

outputs.output_descr: The primary focus of DIPECHO VIII: Strengthening the Resistance of Urban and Rural Communities in South-Eastern Kazakhstan to Seismic Threat is to support and develop innovative approaches to disaster preparedness at local and national level, and to assist the Government of Kazakhstan in strengthening the seismic-risk preparedness system, as well as developing practical methods of involving the public and private sector in seismic-risk management and disaster risk reduction - for nationwide replication by state authorities.
